         <div type="header">
            <p>Verwandtschaftsweisung für Michael und Katharina, Kinder des Michael ChUntter</p>
         </div>                   <div type="entry" resp="rs">
            <p> Einbr. 2 Zg. (Indez: Item frewntschaft Michels des Kunter kinder) <rs type="event"
                  ref="#ev__StB_I_538">An sand Scolastica tag <rs type="fn" role="witness">kam für
                     den rat <rs type="person" ref="#pe__michael_chunter_StB_I_500">Michel der
                           <roleName type="prof" cert="unknown">Chuentter</roleName></rs> und hat da
                     beweist mit <rs type="person" ref="#pe__friedrich_chunter_StB_I_538">Fridreichen
                           <add>den <roleName type="prof" cert="unknown"
                        >Chuenttern</roleName></add></rs> und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__gilg_chunter_StB_I_538">Gilgen den <roleName type="prof"
                           cert="unknown">Chuenttern</roleName></rs></rs>,<rs type="fn"
                     role="recipient">daz <rs type="person" ref="#pe__michael_StB_I_538">seine zway
                           <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__michael_chunter_StB_I_500"
                           >kinder</roleName> Michel <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_500"><add>geswistreid chind</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__elisabeth_StB_I_500"><add>geswistreid
                              chind</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__katharina_StB_I_538">Kathrey <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__michael_chunter_StB_I_500"><add>kinder</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_500"><add>geswistreid
                              chind</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__elisabeth_StB_I_500"><add>geswistreid
                              chind</add></roleName>
                     </rs></rs> mit <rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__niklas_mader_StB_I_500">Niclas des<roleName type="prof"
                           cert="unknown">Mader</roleName></rs></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__katharina_StB_I_500"
                        >zwain <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__niklas_mader_StB_I_500"
                           >kindern</roleName> Kathrein, <rs type="person"
                           ref="#pe__friedrich_chunter_StB_I_538">Fridreichs des Chuentter</rs>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__friedrich_chunter_StB_I_538"
                           >hawsfraw</roleName></rs>, und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__elisabeth_StB_I_500">Elspeten <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__niklas_mader_StB_I_500"><add>kindern</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__michael_StB_I_538">geswistreid
                           chind</roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_538"><add>geswistreid
                              chind</add></roleName>miteinander gewesen sind</rs>.</rs> Als darümb
                  die obgenanten erbern lewt pey irn trewn an aydes stat vor offem rat gesagt
                  habent, als si ze recht solten.</rs> a) hat über der Zeile eingefügt. b) Danach
               leere Stelle. </p>
